{"tid":2078604,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"明愛專上學院開物理治療師 提供逾4萬新生學費資助","createTime":"2020-06-25T07:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:37:30.000Z","uid":225931,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bddb0af9108fb8ad325c0a83ea15bc827b6ef9","tid":2078604,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/RQR2YRCKNOO7PHUJ5HFGSTJJQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FRQR2YRCKNOO7PHUJ5HFGSTJJQI%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=6649a1ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FRQR2YRCKNOO7PHUJ5HFGSTJJQI%2F&h=0f6e97a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/RQR2YRCKNOO7PHUJ5HFGSTJJQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n新課程由健康科學院開辦，第一年將招收50名學生，目前已有近130人報名。梁兆麟指，學院留意到香港的物理治療師人手短缺的問題，加上香港未來人口老化問題越趨嚴重，因此開辦物理治療師的課程。他引述食物及環境衞生局的數據，指到2025年香港將有1100多名物理治療師的短缺，而香港的物理治療師短缺情況一直嚴重，每位物理治療師平均服務2300人，需求殷切。<br />\n<br />\n目前香港有兩間大專學院提供物理治療課程，包括理工大學及東華學院，明愛專上學院將是第三間。公大表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feaf838254c71e9cc4633c8e50657a8ae4399a2","tid":2078604,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1596bdfb2b910187f313031816872eb0c6d745d3","tid":2078604,"uid":205339,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"已爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243dbc3b897733b96088d16382caf2b6f9745380","tid":2078604,"uid":248054,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"公開表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c324ff40672873554d9ce41757bb7b69d0abb2d","tid":2078604,"uid":46685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"243dbc3b897733b96088d16382caf2b6f9745380","tid":2078604,"uid":248054,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"公開表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"理大心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f9b6240a3731b3a5ae5eb7c92053106cba0031","tid":2078604,"uid":304302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"行内人表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a1574e25bcd41346b30bfb4279708ec0a32e54","tid":2078604,"uid":324166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"聽聞PT board 企得好硬 <br />\n有機會要pass 到執業試先肯出牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c562e03f3fe8274216adfccd9ca4b59461505205","tid":2078604,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f74522d9a7186a9078ad415c5f508f75419cc0","tid":2078604,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a1574e25bcd41346b30bfb4279708ec0a32e54","tid":2078604,"uid":324166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"聽聞PT board 企得好硬 <br />\n有機會要pass 到執業試先肯出牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"Pass到好易姐<br />\n讀d野都係一樣"},{"pid":"b4d90dde17ad8339811244baf283df831b75b8c9","tid":2078604,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10: